text: Denis Jacquat (born May 29, 1944 in Thiaucourt-Regniéville, Meurthe-et- Moselle) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Moselle department, and is a member of the Union for a Popular Movement. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:People from Meurthe-et-Moselle Category:Union for French Democracy politicians Category:Republican Party (France) politicians Category:Liberal Democracy (France) politicians Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
